title: Shed Seven - Song Seven (Dutch Treat British Pop ^B077 HQ VBR)
description:
Hi, every time my friend Jamal (yes, the Moroccan) put something on the net (I do not know), I just have to listen. But usually it is quite a lot. So much so, I simply have to rescue the highlights before they fade away into the MEGA bits again. So I took the "best" bits and made a Portrait. And to be honest I hear more music in this group than in Oasis (oops).... Enjoy.
